Unified security scan tool combining Semgrep (source code analysis), SpotBugs+FindSecBugs (bytecode deep analysis), and OSV.dev (component CVE query). Supports 30+ languages. Auto-detects project type and selects optimal engines: Semgrep for source scanning, SpotBugs for Java bytecode deep analysis with cross-file data flow tracking, OSV.dev for component vulnerability lookup against 3000+ CVEs. Use engine='auto' (default) for automatic detection, 'semgrep' for source-only, 'spotbugs' for bytecode-only, or 'osv' for component CVE scanning.
